sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Nadav as Nadav (Director)
    participant Arch as Architect (Opus)
    participant TL as Tech Lead (Opus)
    participant SM as Scrum Master / Team Lead
    participant SrBE as Senior Backend Dev
    participant JrBE as Junior Backend Dev
    participant SrFE as Senior Frontend Dev
    participant QA as QA / Chaos Engineer
    participant Sec as Security Specialist
    participant CR as Code Reviewer
    participant Git as Git Repo

    Nadav->>Arch: Kick off MySMS Messenger (spec + wireframe)
    Arch->>Arch: Draft HLD (scope, IoC/DAL, SMS gateway seam)
    Arch->>Git: commit doc/HLD.md
    Arch->>TL: Handoff HLD

    TL->>TL: Draft tech design + checkpoint plan (CP1-CP12)
    TL->>Git: commit doc/tech-design.md
    TL->>SM: Handoff checkpoint backlog

    SM->>SrBE: Assign CP1, CP2, CP3, CP5 (Rails skeleton, DAL, IoC, identity)
    SM->>SrFE: Assign CP8, CP9, CP10 (Angular skeleton, NewMessage, History)
    par Backend foundation
        SrBE->>Git: commit CP1
        SrBE->>Git: commit CP2
        SrBE->>Git: commit CP3
        SrBE->>Git: commit CP5
    and Frontend foundation
        SrFE->>Git: commit CP8
        SrFE->>Git: commit CP9
        SrFE->>Git: commit CP10
    end
    SrBE-->>SM: Foundation done (flags Container naming fix)
    SrFE-->>SM: Foundation done (flags Chrome-less test env)

    SM->>JrBE: Assign CP4, CP6, CP7, CP12 (gateway, endpoints, CORS/docker)
    SM->>QA: Review completed checkpoints (round 1)
    SM->>Sec: Security review (round 1)
    par Story handoff to QA/Security while dev continues
        JrBE->>Git: commit CP4, CP6, CP7, CP12
        QA->>Git: commit doc/qa-report-round1.md (1 Blocker, 5 Major)
        Sec->>Git: commit doc/security-review-round1.md (1 High, 5 Medium)
    end
    QA-->>SM: Findings report
    Sec-->>SM: Findings report

    SM->>SrBE: Fix backend findings + implement CP11 (Twilio, unverified)
    SM->>SrFE: Fix frontend findings (URL bug, codepoint counter, race)
    par Fix round
        SrBE->>Git: commit fixes + CP11
        SrFE->>Git: commit fixes
    end

    SM->>QA: Re-verify fixes (round 2)
    QA->>Git: commit doc/qa-report-round2.md (8/8 verified-fixed)
    QA-->>SM: Ready for system-wide CR

    loop Loop engineering (capped at $300)
        SM->>CR: System-wide code review
        CR->>Git: commit doc/code-review-iteration-N.md
        CR-->>SM: Verdict (FINDINGS PRESENT or PASS)
        alt Findings present
            SM->>SrBE: Fix findings
            SrBE->>Git: commit fixes
        else PASS
            SM->>Nadav: Loop closed - ready for review
        end
    end

    SM->>Nadav: Delivery: HLD, tech design, working app, QA/security/CR reports, sequence diagram, infographic
